        {
            "id": 6391427,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉拚回3萬4多空交戰激烈 衝高300點後翻黑 矽光子、塑化走揚",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>以色列釋出中東戰事降溫訊號，油價逐步回落，台股今 (20) 日開盤強勁，開 33719.85 點，上漲 30.17 點，隨即一路上攻，最高來到 33989.18 點，漲近 300 點，在權值股紛紛疲軟下，漲幅收斂由紅翻黑，下跌近 150 點，最低來到 33379.24 點，一度跌破 33400 點大關及 10 日均線，早盤估量 1 兆 30 億元。</p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) ，台積電今上漲 10 元，漲約 0.5%，來到 1870 元；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 持平，來到 1680 原，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 持平，維持 1455 元，，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 下跌 0.5%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 跌約 1%。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>矽光子族群仍為盤面焦點，東典光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6588:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6588\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6588-TW</a>)、眾達 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>) 亮紅燈，創威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6530:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6530\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6530-TW</a>) 漲約 9%，上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>)、瑞軒 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2489:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2489\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2489-TW</a>) 均漲約 7%，聯鈞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3450:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3450\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3450-TW</a>)。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美伊戰事帶動塑化類股走強，台達化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1309:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1309\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1309-TW</a>)、華夏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1305:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1305\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1305-TW</a>) 亮紅燈，亞聚 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1308-TW</a>) 漲約 9%，</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
